{"tid":935930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【高鐵】廣州南站下月往港班次減四成","createTime":"2018-12-10T11:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T07:25:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84a5bff2d6209bb372bec4162eea195331319210","tid":935930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵通車超過兩個月，《香港01》發現，內地南下香港的高鐵班次下月起將有所調整，從內地購票網站「12306」網站可見，由下月5日開始，由廣州南站開往西九龍站的班次，從每日34對減至21對，<span style=\"color: red;\">跌幅近四成</span>，連由深圳北站和福田站開出場的班次亦同樣減少。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成未有解釋班次減少的原因，只稱班次是有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/269420/%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5-%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E5%8D%97%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%80%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%AD%E6%AC%A1%E6%B8%9B%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E5%8A%89%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%90-%E7%8F%AD%E6%AC%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%A2%9E%E7%84%A1%E6%B8%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F269420%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2588%2590-%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A2%259E%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B8%259B&d=wmRl8O2Sve2obXbrhbLjENU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=25068d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/269420/%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5-%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E5%8D%97%E7%AB%99%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%80%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%AD%E6%AC%A1%E6%B8%9B%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E5%8A%89%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%90-%E7%8F%AD%E6%AC%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%A2%9E%E7%84%A1%E6%B8%9B</a>"},{"pid":"e261cedb760faa6604686e243d696f15280adc88","tid":935930,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\